TY  - JOUR
TI  - Analysis of Models for Commercial Fishing: Mathematical and Economical Aspects
AU  - Leung, Anthony
AU  - Wang, Ar-Young
AB  - [This paper investigates a simple economic model for the commercial fishing industry. The results imply the phenomena of non-explosive fishing capital investment and non-extinctive fishery resources. Both investments and resources will always tend to an equilibrium position. A comparison with a more general model is also made.]
