TY  - JOUR
TI  - Discriminating among Linear Models with Interdependent Disturbances
AU  - Gaver, Kenneth M.
AU  - Geisel, Martin S.
AB  - [A Bayesian procedure for comparing linear models with non-scalar covariance matrices is developed. For the case of first order auto-regressive disturbances, an approximate expression for the error in the posterior odds due to ignoring the serial correlation is given, and it's accuracy is investigated via sampling experiments.]
